vocatnet.ro}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asociatiapavel.ro/parinti-educatia.php|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112210625/http://www.asociatiapavel.ro/parinti-educatia.php|url-status=dead|archive-date=12 January 2015|title=Asociatia P.A.V.E.L.|date=12 January 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[#Russia|Russia]]\n| Legal since 1992, law sometimes ignored. Every home schooled child must be enrolled into a state-licensed school (can be a private school), and does not have to pass annual exams. Home schooled children received diplomas from supervising school.\n| 50,000-100,000\n| [[Education in Russia|WP]]{{Circular reference|date=February 2019}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.familyeducation.ru/?module=articles&c=Diff&b=1&a=1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217155140/http://www.familyeducation.ru/?module=articles&c=Diff&b=1&a=1|url-status=dead|archive-date=17 December 2016|title=\u0421\u0435\u043c\u0435\u0439\u043d\u043e\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435, \u0414\u043e\u043c\u0430\u0448\u043d\u0435\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435, \u042d\u043a\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\u043d\u0430\u0442 - \u041e \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0435\u043a\u0442\u0435|date=17 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hslda.org/content/hs/international/Russia/201704040.asp|title=HSLDA - Why Homeschooling is Gaining Respect in Russia|author=|date=|website=hslda.org}}</ref>\n|-\n| San Marino\n| Illegal, public education is mandatory without known exceptions.\n| Virtually no homeschooling*\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nationsencyclopedia.com/Europe/San-Marino-EDUCATION.html|title=Education - San Marino|author=|date=|website=www.nationsencyclopedia.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[#Serbia|Serbia]]\n| Legal.\n| Unknown\n| <ref>http://www.mpn.gov.rs/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/\u0417\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d-\u043e-\u043e\u0441\u043d\u043e\u0432\u043d\u043e\u043c-\u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\