ie-2011-privind-scolarizarea-la-domiciliu-respectiv-infiintarea-de-grupe-clase-in-spitale-emitent-ministerul-educatiei-132840.html|title=METODOLOGIE - CADRU din 7 octombrie 2011 privind scolarizarea la domiciliu, respectiv infiintarea de grupe/clase in spitale|author=|date=|website=www.monitoruljuridic.ro}}</ref><ref>http://legestart.ro/Metodologia-2011-cadru-scolarizarea-domiciliu-respectiv-infiintarea-grupe-clase-spitale-%28NTk0Njk2%29.htm{{Dead link|date=May 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.avocatnet.ro/articol_26837/Ordinul-MECTS-nr-5575-2011-aprobarea-Metodologiei-cadru-privind-scolarizarea-la-domiciliu.html|title=Ordinul MECTS nr. 5.575/2011 - aprobarea Metodologiei-cadru privind scolarizarea la domiciliu|first=|last=Avocatnet.ro|date=|website=www.avocatnet.ro}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asociatiapavel.ro/parinti-educatia.php|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112210625/http://www.asociatiapavel.ro/parinti-educatia.php|url-status=dead|archive-date=12 January 2015|title=Asociatia P.A.V.E.L.|date=12 January 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[#Russia|Russia]]\n| Legal since 1992, law sometimes ignored. Every home schooled child must be enrolled into a state-licensed school (can be a private school), and does not have to pass annual exams. Home schooled children received diplomas from supervising school.\n| 50,000-100,000\n| [[Education in Russia|WP]]{{Circular reference|date=February 2019}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.familyeducation.ru/?module=articles&c=Diff&b=1&a=1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217155140/http://www.familyeducation.ru/?module=articles&c=Diff&b=1&a=1|url-status=dead|archive-date=17 December 2016|title=\u0421\u0435\u043c\u0435\u0439\u043d\u043e\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435, \u0414\u043e\u043c\u0430\u0448\u043d\u0435\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435, \u042d\u043a\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\